descriptionHtml:
This is the character that I have used since Skyrim was released. 
Uses Hjerim as the main home, has lots of gear stored in that house, just look around and in all the containers.

May be added into the Skyrim Immersion Mod found at http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=8228

Be warned: most quests have been finished and the save may unlock all but one of the achievements for skyrim.

Thanks to AmethystDeceiver for their amazing Black Sacrament armor found here
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=5696
author: taitn
